  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "collatz",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/collatz/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.57,
      "size": 25200,
      "text": "有一个游戏，规则简单到小学生都会玩。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "collatz",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/collatz/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "随便选一个正整数，按两条规则不停地变换它。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "collatz",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/collatz/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.24,
      "size": 35856,
      "text": "奇怪的是，无论从哪里出发，最后似乎都会掉进同一个终点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "collatz",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "rule-1",
      "filename": "rule-rule-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/collatz/xiaoxiao/rule-rule-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.25,
      "size": 20016,
      "text": "如果这个数是偶数，就把它除以 2。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "collatz",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "rule-2",
      "filename": "rule-rule-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/collatz/xiaoxiao/rule-rule-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.32,
      "size": 21168,
      "text": "如果是奇数，就把它乘以 3 再加 1。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "collatz",
      "section_id": "rule",
      "line_id": "rule-3",
      "filename": "rule-rule-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/collatz/xiaoxiao/rule-rule-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "得到新数后，重复判断奇偶，再走对应的那条路。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "collatz",
      "section_id": "hail",
      "line_id": "hail-1",
      "filename": "hail-hail-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/collatz/xiaoxiao/hail-hail-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
      "size": 31824,
      "text": "数值会像冰雹一样，忽而冲上高空，忽而急速下坠。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "collatz",
      "section_id": "hail",
      "line_id": "hail-2",
      "filename": "hail-hail-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/collatz/xiaoxiao/hail-hail-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "从 27 出发，它一路飙升到九千多，再慢慢跌回来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "collatz",
      "section_id": "hail",
      "line_id": "hail-3",
      "filename": "hail-hail-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/collatz/xiaoxiao/hail-hail-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.58,
      "size": 25344,
      "text": "正因如此，这些数被亲切地称为“冰雹数”。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "collatz",
      "section_id": "mystery",
      "line_id": "mys-1",
      "filename": "mystery-mys-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/collatz/xiaoxiao/mystery-mys-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "人们已经验证了极其庞大的数字，全都乖乖回到了 1。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "collatz",
      "section_id": "mystery",
      "line_id": "mys-2",
      "filename": "mystery-mys-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/collatz/xiaoxiao/mystery-mys-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.66,
      "size": 26496,
      "text": "可是没有人能证明：所有正整数都一定归 1。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "collatz",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/collatz/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.45,
      "size": 23184,
      "text": "输入一个起点，看它的轨迹如何起伏。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "collatz",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/collatz/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.0,
      "size": 31968,
      "text": "数一数需要多少步才落到 1，那就是它的停止时间。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "collatz",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/collatz/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "偶数减半，奇数三倍加一，规则简单到极点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "collatz",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/collatz/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "轨迹却像冰雹般难以预测，是否总归 1 仍是悬案。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "collatz",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/collatz/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.72,
      "size": 27504,
      "text": "简单的规则藏着最深的谜题，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
